  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Alzheimer's
Type:        Neurological
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Aging/genetics
Symptoms:    Memory loss, confusion
Treatment:   No cure; slowing medications
Deaths/yr:   0.12M
Vaccine:     No
Discovered:  1906

Disease:     COVID-19
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    SARS-CoV-2
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, cough, loss of smell
Treatment:   Antivirals, supportive care
Deaths/yr:   5.0M
Vaccine:     Yes (mRNA vaccines)
Discovered:  2019

Disease:     Influenza
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Influenza viruses
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, chills, muscle aches
Treatment:   Oseltamivir, rest, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     Yes (annual update)
Discovered:  1933

